By Cassia Pianca, Piero Mazzini, John Largier and Toby Garfield</p>

  <p><strong>“The impact of wind-forcing on the Thermal Wind Shear of a river plume”</strong> <br />
By Piero Mazzini, Robert J. Chant, John Wilkin, Nick Nidzieko, Malcolm Scully and Elias Hunter</p>

